-- Vocal Shortcuts batch importer
-- Generated by bin/dictation-commands-vocal-shortcuts-import.py
-- Walks System Settings → Accessibility → Speech → Vocal Shortcuts
-- and adds one phrase → Shortcut binding per Sal command.
-- 
-- Prerequisites:
--   1. Apple Silicon Mac (Vocal Shortcuts is unavailable on Intel)
--   2. macOS 15.0 or later
--   3. All 588 Sal Shortcuts already imported into Shortcuts.app
--   4. UI scripting permission granted to Script Editor
-- 
-- This script is conservative: it pauses between each binding so the user
-- can monitor progress and abort with Cmd-. if the UI drifts.

